 at det var uforsvarlig at legen ble fastlege for pasienten, skriver Skorpen i brevet til helsetilsynet.", "Statens helsetilsyn har gitt svar at den skal gi en avklaring innen seks m\u00e5neder. Tilsynet var ikke tilgjengelig for ytterligere kommentar."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "d417d560eafb96c07fbcaabd1d6e6aceb0b5dacbe342ad439d4af6175c5b7d28"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-07-20T07:26:37.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Lege i S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag suspendert etter beskyldninger om seksuell omgang med pasient."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9881731.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_tas050712_MarianneH__2_1_T152B403.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d4f9a7a31e5b381351e1d27195b07c5c4be2df5e.jpg?59705b2d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Lege siktet for sexovergrep -adressa.no", "Misbruk av stilling", "Kommunen meldte fra", "Til Statens helsetilsyn"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "d4f9a7a31e5b381351e1d27195b07c5c4be2df5e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["pasient", "lege", "seksuell omgang"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["fylkesmannen", "statens"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "m\u00f8re og romsdal"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["anders skorpen", "marianne h\u00f8yer"]}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": 